253
00:22:26,050 --> 00:22:32,194
It's a peaceful moment allowing to dive into characters' state of mind, Max, Chris or Sean,

254
00:22:32,194 --> 00:22:34,295
and learn more about their feelings.

255
00:22:34,295 --> 00:22:40,159
The player will hear voiceover but also enjoy new camera angle and music.

256
00:22:40,159 --> 00:22:46,484
Those moments of contemplation and nostalgia are optional and are a reward for the curious

257
00:22:46,484 --> 00:22:47,905
players who take their time.

258
00:22:49,165 --> 00:22:54,208
For each of them, we have edited a unique remix of Jonathan's score, based on the situation,

259
00:22:54,208 --> 00:22:56,689
the writing, and also the mood of the scene.

260
00:22:56,689 --> 00:23:03,793
The example we are going to show you is coming from the fourth episode of Life is Strange 1.

