00:25:43,290 --> 00:25:51,854
As our games are episodic, the menu is really important for us because it's a way to bring the player back in the universe of the game.

278
00:25:51,854 --> 00:25:59,517
As you can see, on the left is changed one menu, the background view and the ambient sound are evolving, but the music is staying the same.

279
00:25:59,517 --> 00:26:04,399
The strong main theme of the game linked all those different menus together.

280
00:26:28,893 --> 00:26:33,922
For the second opus we wanted to begin with something very similar to Lefty Strange 1

281
00:26:33,922 --> 00:26:37,970
with a folk vibe and this neighborhood feeling.

282
00:26:37,970 --> 00:26:40,495
So at the beginning of the first episode you will have this menu.

283
00:26:42,239 --> 00:26:47,321
After the terrible incident in Seattle, we wanted to break everything the player and

284
00:26:47,321 --> 00:26:48,882
