00:33:07,902 --> 00:33:12,765
Nesson saying I'm sorry, which is very emotional when you know the guy.

346
00:33:12,765 --> 00:33:16,387
Max's reaction to the fact that those are his last words.

347
00:33:16,387 --> 00:33:21,870
And of course the destruction of the town the moment Max exits the car and the player

348
00:33:21,870 --> 00:33:22,711
