395
00:37:24,191 --> 00:37:28,572
So we'll take the example of the Awesome Adventures of Captain Spirit.

396
00:37:28,572 --> 00:37:34,755
The process is a bit different in this case because we are able to use a track in a new way.

397
00:37:34,755 --> 00:37:38,556
Not just having an existing song on top of images.

398
00:37:38,556 --> 00:37:42,098
We can reduce the volume of one instrument, create a new mix.

399
00:37:42,678 --> 00:37:45,180
cut or create loops for a choice for example,

400
00:37:45,180 --> 00:37:51,605
it's incredible for us to have access to this level of interactivity on an existing song.

401
00:37:51,605 --> 00:37:56,930
Of course, what is really important in this case is to keep the spirit of the song,

402
00:37:56,930 --> 00:37:59,892
its strength and to preserve the will of the artist.

403
00:37:59,892 --> 00:38:02,014
As we can do all the changes we want,

404
00:38:02,014 --> 00:38:05,397
we have to be careful to respect the original work of the musician.

405
00:38:06,708 --> 00:38:11,474
So we'll take the example of the song Death With Dignity from Sufjan Stevens,

406
00:38:11,474 --> 00:38:15,199
